      "title": "Two Russian crude oil ships arrive",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Power and Energy, two Russian Urals crude oil ships are scheduled to arrive in Sri Lanka. Among them, the minister said that a ship carrying 100,000 metric tons of crude oil will reach Colombo tonight.",
        "In addition, the minister said on his Twitter account that another ship carrying 120,000 metric tons of crude oil is scheduled to reach Sri Lanka between the 23rd and 29th."
      ],
